{"word":"ἀνέκαθεν","slug":"ἀνέκαθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνέκαθεν</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀνεκάς'><el>ἀνεκάς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> of Place, <i>from above</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of Time, <i>from the first, by origin</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; so with <a href='S:Article'>Art.</a>, <el>τὸ ἀνέκαθεν</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}